---
// Reusable one-line affiliate disclosure banner.
// Drop this at the top of any resource/affiliate page so the disclosure
// is visible before any affiliate links appear.
---

<div class="border-y border-clay-200 bg-clay-50/70">
  <div class="container-wide py-2.5 text-center text-xs text-clay-800 sm:text-sm">
    <p>
      This page contains affiliate links. <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/" class="font-medium underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-clay-950">See our disclosure</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
